title: Spectacular Oceanfront Home Staircase to the Beach 15366
text:
Spectacular Oceanfront Home Staircase to the Beach 15366 ad date: 09/30/2015 
Staircase to the Beach 15366 Oceanview Dr., Brookings Welcome to your gracious home with garden entry, a world of windows and oak flooring. Open floor plan includes sunny kitchen with breakfast bar, granite counters, generous cabinets and outdoor dining. Spacious 3 BR 2 1/2 BA 2,357 sq. ft. on 1-level. Master suite with access to rear paver patio and beautiful back yard. Easy maintenance with tile roof, cement siding, built-in vac and sprinklers.
